{"tid":1604681,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港島人同我入曬黎！！勇派修頓、和派銅鑼灣","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T05:48:20.000Z","uid":244636,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e49bb8035fd744b0231b7e45609c3c20b6dc734","tid":1604681,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"人數好緊要 ！<span style=\"color: red;\">港島人ASSEMBLE！</span><br />\n九龍人已經唔會黎港島<br />\n港島灣仔站要好好整理<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lsquo;勇&rsquo;派 有前線經驗係修頓</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lsquo;和&rsquo;派 係銅鑼灣集結做最強後盾掩護</span></strong>做back up 做cover 又唔駛阻住衝衝子<br />\n<br />\n金鐘個邊真係唔建議作退路 <br />\n狗總 政總 大把位比佢地部處 再突襲都得 <br />\n<br />\n我知好多人真係見到tg放題 濫捕 好驚 我都係<br />\n但又好唔甘心好想出 <br />\n唔好驚 我地無野可以輸<br />\n唔好比籍口自己唔出<br />\n同屋企人講 請佢地做我地既back up 銅鑼灣見<br />\n聽日全世界出街街同我<span style=\"color: red;\">賀佢老母</span><br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n著<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全黑、帶背囊</span></strong> 保護前線 （帶多套衫）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">帶長遮！帶水！</span></strong>帶口罩！<br />\n（落樓下五金包買豬嘴 唔敢講就問 有冇6200/6800面罩、眼罩、防割手套）"},{"pid":"20cab85ec5ce05efba3753f3415ed5da7033e437","tid":1604681,"uid":244636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoQ0Knr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoQ0Knr.jpg&h=f82a9547&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7764170fb2bb43307527458b4222ef1057f0f1de","tid":1604681,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:49.000Z","msg":"10月1 賀佢老母"},{"pid":"c91de59f801db1eb989931c4a89d526794755236","tid":1604681,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 